ww.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/M%E1%BA%ABu-%C4%91%C6%A1n/poem-QdW4oHZhqvh7eaeB12ZqEw">Mẫu đơn - 牡丹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Qu%E1%BB%91c/T%C3%A2y-h%E1%BB%93-xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt/poem-0cNx70K34-TWlA0ALUgIQw">Tây hồ xuân nhật - 西湖春日</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-An-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-CZX4A7xNs4WPs3fFDSW8Cg">Vương An Quốc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/Th%C3%A1nh-Tuy%E1%BB%81n-y%E1%BA%BFn/poem-6izvYONcqK0i0WUFX0IpHg">Thánh Tuyền yến - 聖泉宴</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%E1%BB%99t/author-_ZqxSvkbsUwNbnMEINI85Q">Vương Bột</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-K%E1%BB%B7-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/T%E1%BB%91-trung-t%C3%ACnh/poem-uCWogTdF6jgqTVUlZsnz0A">Tố trung tình - 訴衷情</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C3%81n-K%E1%BB%B7-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o/author-P5gHWt0svykQZv94RUMFeg">Án Kỷ Đạo</a>)<br></div>	</div>
